# ── Supabase (passwordless email-OTP auth + data) ────────────────────────────
# Create ONE Supabase project and use it for BOTH apps (mlr-app + family-fest)
# so a person is one account everywhere — see NEXT-STEPS.md §3.
#
# Find these in the Supabase dashboard → Project Settings → API.
# The anon key is PUBLIC-SAFE (protected by Row Level Security), so it's fine
# to ship in the static bundle / store as a GitHub repo Variable.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill in real values.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=YOUR-ANON-PUBLIC-KEY
